Release Notes
Based on Trend Reversal Alert Hybrid [TRAH] indicator which is a hybrid script of simple reversal strategy trading and Fibonacci levels. This version in comparison to Trend-Reversal-Alerts-Strategy-lite makes it possible to fine-tune the parameters. Version update from 2nd to 6th.
